{"title":"誓为革命治海河  海河工地诗选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓为革命治海河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海河工地诗选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北省人民响应毛主席“一定要根治海河”的伟大号召，在今年春季继续投入黑龙港地区的工程建设。治河民工和干部们在施工现场上忘我地劳动，把毛主席的号召当作他们行动的指南，创造了不少奇迹。他们在劳动中还拿起笔杆子，创作了不少文艺作品，歌颂我们伟大的党，歌颂我们伟大的领袖毛主席。他们不仅是一支生产革命大军，而且是一支文化革命大军。这是在毛泽东思想光辉照耀下出现的崭新的革命气象。　编　者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席号召震天地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗建国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清凉江上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗招展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐奋战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一定要根治海河”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决征服自然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席号召震天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄立志绣河山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心似火热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志比石坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕崖高坡陡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕风吹天寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锨镐舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小车转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖开地下三尺土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疏通河道挽狂澜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱除洪涝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭盐碱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺高产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造福子孙万代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国永是春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听党的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘明科"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锨听我的话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席一句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地筑起千里坝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民工离不开毛主席的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李希彦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两棵柱子一棵梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五棵檩条搭间房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中央挂上毛主席象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一副对联贴两旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工棚摆满毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录贴满墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚工棚灯光闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民工都学“毛选”忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民工离不开毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色民工红思想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录发给我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏幸合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录发给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的关怀暖心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉起车子望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓为革命治海河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录发给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海航行有了舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活学活用心底亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排涝除碱灭灾祸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录发给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随身携带贴心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完全、彻底为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施工场上唱新歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录发给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中燃起革命火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下“愚公”移山志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海也敢过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好奖章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩国祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好奖章挂胸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起心海千层浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席画出幸福图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给海河换新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞针走线党指引，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福花开万年香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我做的工作比针尖小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给的荣誉比线还长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是我生来骨头硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是我长就志气昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作万度热呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼得我志在革命身如钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好奖章闪红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民工个个干劲长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推土专爱登高坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命步伐永向上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢锨就是我的枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西辛店通讯组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根治海河把阵上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢锨就是我的枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞车舞锨斗志高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大河见我把路让。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士用枪去打仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用钢锨挖河床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士用枪保江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给海河换新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泽有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的号令一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治河大军出了庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车子铁锨一排排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万大军浩荡荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘扬迎朝日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步伐整齐歌嘹亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营盘横扎五百里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开工号子长空扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分兵布阵斗老天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锨挥舞闪银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下治水英雄志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢叫海河换新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战字歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘百川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑龙港畔旗漫卷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众健儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐把神通显。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银锨飞舞土车转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊回首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推出一座山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治河再创新史篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让“黑龙”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此听使唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢锨在手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五尺钢锨握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身是力精神抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根治海河当硬汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵着黑龙鼻子走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖开硬土层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修好排水沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手写下壮志篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社年年是丰收。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}